<!DOCTYPE html>
<body>
    <main role="main">
        <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1" class=""></li>
                <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2" class=""></li>
            </ol>
            <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide" data-mdb-ride="carousel">
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <img id="first_slide"
                             src="~/images/University-Of-Utah-Warnock-Engineering-Building_Banner-1_Images-for-Dev.png" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img id="second_slide"
                             src="https://d1bbnjcim4wtri.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/01105300/Winter-Health-Campus-View-2018-7-2048x1366.jpg"
                             style="overflow: hidden; z-index: 1; object-fit: cover;" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img id="third_slide"
                             src="~/images/Library.png" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                </a>
                <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
                    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                    <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Marketing messaging and featurettes
        ================================================== -->
        <!-- Wrap the rest of the page in another container to center all the content. -->

        <div class="container marketing">

            <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <img class="rounded-circle" src="~/images/Web Form.png" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
                    <h2>Get Started</h2>
                    <p>Applying for TA? Click here to fill out your application form now!</p>
                    <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#" role="button">View details »</a></p>
                </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <img class="rounded-circle" src="~/images/Confused.png" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
                    <h2>FAQ</h2>
                    <p>Have any questions? Take a look here at the frequently most asked questions to see if your question resides here.</p>
                    <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#" role="button">View details »</a></p>
                </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <img class="rounded-circle" src="~/images/About Us.png" alt="People standing on a globe that says 'About Us'" width="140" height="140">
                    <h2>About Us</h2>
                    <p>Find out more about what it is like to be a TA for the University of Utah</p>
                    <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#" role="button">View details »</a></p>
                </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
            </div><!-- /.row -->
            <!-- START THE FEATURETTES -->

            <hr class="featurette-divider">

            <div class="row featurette">
                <div class="col-md-7">
                    <h2 class="featurette-heading">Connect with students.</h2>
                    <p class="lead">To be a TA, you need to learn how to build a trusting relationship with students. Students need someone that they can have faith and rely on when they need help. </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-5">
                    <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" data-src="holder.js/500x500/auto" alt="TA and Student studying together" style="width: 500px; height: 500px;" src="~/images/Students Studying.jpg" data-holder-rendered="true">
                </div>
            </div>

            <hr class="featurette-divider">

            <div class="row featurette">
                <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
                    <h2 class="featurette-heading">Help their progression grow.</h2>
                    <p class="lead">Sure you can become a TA to earn a simple paycheck, but nothing is more rewarding than watching the students you help grow and become more successful.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
                    <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" data-src="holder.js/500x500/auto" alt="Girl standing outside next to arrows pointing up to show progression" src="~/images/Portrait with Arrows Pointing Up.jpg" data-holder-rendered="true" style="width: 500px; height: 500px;">
                </div>
            </div>

            <hr class="featurette-divider">

            <div class="row featurette">
                <div class="col-md-7">
                    <h2 class="featurette-heading">Guide them to graduate.</span></h2>
                    <p class="lead">Students have the same end goal that you have too. Help them reach that goal and let you and their hardwork pay off!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-5">
                    <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" data-src="holder.js/500x500/auto" alt="A graudate student from the University of Utah" src="~/images/Utah Graduate.jpg" data-holder-rendered="true" style="width: 500px; height: 500px;">
                </div>
            </div>

            <hr class="featurette-divider">

            <!-- /END THE FEATURETTES -->

        </div><!-- /.container -->
    </main>
</body>
